	<h1 class="title">「这世界」发现了一种稀有的鸟，可以为了科学杀死一只做标本吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4695/small/4695.jpg?1418026962" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙若空 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-12 12:15:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15951/medium/15951.jpg?1444619441" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15951" data-title="《「这世界」发现了一种稀有的鸟，可以为了科学杀死一只做标本吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15951/medium/15951.jpg?1444619441" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15951.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
